Package no.ntnu.idatx1005.model.task

Class Task

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatx1005.model.task.Task
public class Task extends Object

Represents a task.

A task has a unique id, a name, a description, a due date, a priority, and a task weight. The task can also have a list of assigned users.

Since:
V0.1.0
Author:
Hector Mendana Morales, William Holtsdalen
